HEY LIEUTENANT!

689
01:02:41,567 --> 01:02:44,267
S'IL VOUS PLAIT,
LIEUTENANT.

690
01:02:44,334 --> 01:02:48,000
HE DOESN'T BELIEVE I AM WITH
YOU. WE ARE IN THE SAME CONVOY.

691
01:02:48,067 --> 01:02:50,300
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
- IS HE WITH YOU?

692
01:02:51,200 --> 01:02:54,467
- THE SAME CONVOY!
- SHUT UP...

693
01:02:54,534 --> 01:02:56,033
AND LET
THE WHITE MAN TALK.

694
01:02:59,734 --> 01:03:04,400
- ARE THESE PEOPLE WITH YOU?
- OUR CONVOY IS THE JEEPS AND THE TRUCKS.

695
01:03:04,467 --> 01:03:06,434
I'M SORRY.
I'VE ORDERS...

696
01:03:06,501 --> 01:03:08,467
ONLY EXPATRIATES.

697
01:03:15,601 --> 01:03:18,334
GO! GO!
REMOVE THAT THING!

698
01:03:18,400 --> 01:03:19,934
GO!

699
01:03:49,033 --> 01:03:51,033
XAVIER MUYANGO?

700
01:03:55,033 --> 01:03:57,601
WHO IS XAVIER MUYANGO?

701
01:03:58,968 --> 01:04:01,100
I AM.

702
01:04:07,901 --> 01:04:09,901
AREN'T YOU THE TRAITOR

703
01:04:09,968 --> 01:04:12,567
XAVIER MUYANGO WE'VE HEARD
ABOUT ON THE RADIO?

704
01:04:16,234 --> 01:04:17,834
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU MEAN.

705
01:04:17,901 --> 01:04:19,834
MOVE OVER WITH THAT GROUP.

706
01:04:19,901 --> 01:04:22,601
EVERYBODY ELSE,
GET OFF. GET OFF!

707
01:04:22,667 --> 01:04:25,434
GET OVER, GET OVER!

708
01:04:29,100 --> 01:04:31,167
WHAT'S WRONG
WITH YOU, EH?

709
01:04:31,234 --> 01:04:34,234
- MOVE OVER! FORGET SOMETHING?
- I CAN SPEAK FOR THIS MAN!

710
01:04:34,300 --> 01:04:36,567
HE IS LOYAL.
HE IS A GOOD SOLDIER.

711
01:04:36,634 --> 01:04:38,634
THE ARMY IS FILLED
WITH TRAITORS.

712
01:04:38,701 --> 01:04:40,901
THEN I WILL TAKE HIM
TO THE HEADQUARTERS MYSELF.

713
01:04:40,968 --> 01:04:43,200
- I'LL TAKE...
- YOU WANT TO HELP?

714
01:04:43,267 --> 01:04:46,467
YOU WANT TO HELP?

715
01:04:46,534 --> 01:04:48,534
- GIVE HIM A MACHETE.
- NO.

716
01:04:58,901 --> 01:05:02,634
WE DON'T WASTE BULLETS
ON COCKROACH TRAITORS.

717
01:05:07,934 --> 01:05:09,501
AUGUSTIN,

718
01:05:35,801 --> 01:05:37,834
XAVIER... XAVIER...

719
01:05:39,901 --> 01:05:41,968
MUYANGO.

720
01:05:47,667 --> 01:05:50,000
MUYANGO,
STAND UP!

721
01:06:04,000 --> 01:06:05,934
COME ON,
LET'S GO.

722
01:06:06,000 --> 01:06:08,133
LET'S GO.
IT'S NOT GONNA HELP.

723
01:06:08,200 --> 01:06:10,434
- SH... HEY, HEY! HEY!
- LET'S GO, LET'S GO.

724
01:06:13,334 --> 01:06:15,734
- HEY!
- IT'S NOT GONNA HELP. HE'S DEAD.

725
01:06:46,100 --> 01:06:48,200
- OUl?
- Colonel Bagosora,

726
01:06:48,267 --> 01:06:50,334
THIS IS ASSISTANT
SECRETARY BUSHNELL.

727
01:06:50,400 --> 01:06:52,834
MRS. BUSHNELL,
WHAT A WONDERFUL SURPRISE.

728
01:06:52,901 --> 01:06:56,467
I REGRET WE DIDN'T MEET DURING
YOUR LAST VISIT IN KIGALI.

729
01:06:56,534 --> 01:06:58,634
SIR, I'M CALLING TO ADVISE YOU

730
01:06:58,701 --> 01:07:01,267
THAT WE VIEW THE SITUATION
VERY SERIOUSLY.

731
01:07:01,334 --> 01:07:03,534
PRESIDENT CLINTON
IS VERY CONCERNED.

732
01:07:03,601 --> 01:07:05,667
HOW KIND OF THE PRESIDENT
TO BE THINKING OF ME.

733
01:07:05,734 --> 01:07:09,167
WE HAVE RECEIVED REPORTS
THAT THERE HAS BEEN...

734
01:07:09,234 --> 01:07:12,601
THE U.N. REPORTS ARE VERY EXAGGERATED.
THERE HAS BEEN SOME TROUBLE.

735
01:07:12,667 --> 01:07:14,734
AND NATURALLY, WE HAVE
TO DEFEND OUR PEOPLE.

736
01:07:14,801 --> 01:07:18,567
YOU MUST TAKE ACTION TO
CHANGE THE COURSE OF EVENTS.

737
01:07:18,634 --> 01:07:20,767
BUT IT'S THE REBELS,
THEY ATTACKED US.

738
01:07:20,834 --> 01:07:23,367
AND NOW THE PEOPLE HAVE
RISEN UP TO DEFEND THEMSELVES.

739
01:07:23,434 --> 01:07:26,367
COLONEL, WE KNOW WHO'S
PERPETRATING THESE KILLINGS.

740
01:07:26,434 --> 01:07:28,467
YOU CAN SEE ALL THE WAY
FROM WASHINGTON?

741
01:07:28,534 --> 01:07:30,300
MRS. BUSHNELL,

742
01:07:30,367 --> 01:07:33,100
IF THERE WAS A CSEFIRE WE
MIGHT BE ABLE TO DO SOMETHING,

743
01:07:33,167 --> 01:07:35,300
but now the situation
is very difficult.

744
01:07:35,367 --> 01:07:37,801
VERY DIFFICULT, MADAME.
YOU CAN'T IMAGINE.

745
01:07:37,868 --> 01:07:40,634
NO, YOU DO NOT NEED
A CEASEFIRE

746
01:07:40,701 --> 01:07:44,501
TO STOP THIS
HATE RADIO BROADCAST.

747
01:07:44,567 --> 01:07:46,501
MONSIEUR BAGOSORA,

748
01:07:46,567 --> 01:07:49,467
IF YOU DO NOT STOP THE KILLING,
THERE WILL BE CONSEQUENCES.

749
01:07:49,534 --> 01:07:51,467
REALLY?

750
01:07:51,534 --> 01:07:53,300
YOU WILL SEND
THE MARINES?

751
01:07:53,367 --> 01:07:55,234
WE HAVE NO OIL HERE.
WE HAVE NO DIAMONDS.

752
01:07:55,300 --> 01:07:57,834
WE HAVE NOTHING YOU NEED IN
RWANDA. WHY WOULD YOU COME?

753
01:07:57,901 --> 01:08:00,234
IF YOU DO NOT
CEASE THE KILLINGS,

754
01:08:00,300 --> 01:08:02,000
I PROMISE YOU,

755
01:08:02,067 --> 01:08:05,000
YOU WILL BE HELD
PERSONALLY RESPONSIBLE.

756
01:08:06,868 --> 01:08:08,868
I WILL SEE
WHAT WE CAN DO.

757
01:08:20,801 --> 01:08:23,167
MAMA, MAMA!

